artworks.title: Lunar Dreams
artworks.description: A dreamlike celestial collage featuring vintage portraiture surrounded by lunar phases and cosmic elements. Created for an indie musician's debut album, this piece captures the ethereal quality of nocturnal contemplation.

seo.metaTitle: Lunar Dreams - Surreal Digital Collage by Jolene Casko
seo.metaDescription: A dreamlike celestial collage featuring vintage portraiture surrounded by lunar phases and cosmic elements.
seo.altText: Vintage portrait surrounded by moons and stars in purple celestial hues

artworks.title: Rose Garden
artworks.description: An ethereal composition blending vintage roses with dreamlike atmospheric elements. This piece explores themes of memory and the passage of time through layered botanical imagery.

seo.metaTitle: Rose Garden - Ethereal Floral Collage by Jolene Casko
seo.metaDescription: An ethereal composition blending vintage roses with dreamlike atmospheric elements.
seo.altText: Ethereal floral collage with vintage roses in dreamy atmosphere

artworks.title: Metamorphosis
artworks.description: A visual exploration of transformation through layered imagery and unexpected juxtapositions. This experimental piece pushes the boundaries of traditional collage into abstract territory.

seo.metaTitle: Metamorphosis - Abstract Transformative Collage by Jolene Casko
seo.metaDescription: A visual exploration of transformation through layered imagery and unexpected juxtapositions.

artworks.title: Cosmic Ocean
artworks.description: Where cosmic vastness meets oceanic depth in a surreal meditation on infinity. Commissioned for an ambient electronic music project, this piece explores the parallels between celestial and aquatic realms.

seo.metaTitle: Cosmic Ocean - Celestial & Oceanic Collage by Jolene Casko
seo.metaDescription: Where cosmic vastness meets oceanic depth in a surreal meditation on infinity.
seo.altText: Celestial and oceanic collage merging cosmic and aquatic elements

artworks.title: Stardust
artworks.description: A vintage portrait reimagined through cosmic stardust and celestial wonder. This personal work explores the intersection of human presence and infinite space.

seo.metaTitle: Stardust - Vintage Portrait with Cosmic Elements by Jolene Casko
seo.metaDescription: A vintage portrait reimagined through cosmic stardust and celestial wonder.
seo.altText: Vintage portrait with cosmic stardust and celestial elements

artworks.title: Symphony
artworks.description: A visual symphony translating musical layers into surreal collage composition. Commissioned for a classical crossover project, this piece captures the complexity and emotional depth of orchestral music.

seo.metaTitle: Symphony - Musical Inspired Collage by Jolene Casko
seo.metaDescription: A visual symphony translating musical layers into surreal collage composition.
seo.altText: Musical inspired collage translating orchestral complexity
